metadata.name: Sprout of Creativity 'BLUE'
metadata.description:
Sometimes the one thing that can help push through blank page syndrome is just a tiny seed of creativity.  A seed that with love and care sprouts into a beautiful artistic creation!

This piece is an ode to the process of artistic creation and the celebration of fighting through imposter syndrome, persevering and bringing to life through the manifestation of our combined influences and experiences a work of art.

May this little sprout help you in your creative endeavors and remind you that you already have everything you need to contribute something positive to the world!

All assets custom created by Eyedesyn. 

Uncompressed version and PFP image available upon request. 1080x1920px, mp4, 11s, 345 frames, 29.97 FPS, seamless loop

Created by EJ Hassenfratz January 2022
